Enum PieceType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PieceType>

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<PieceType>
    public enum PieceType
extends java.lang.Enum<PieceType>
    Enumeration of the differen piece types. Values are included for scoring purposes, using the typical values, but 40 for the King.

      • getSteps

        public Direction[][] getSteps()
        Returns the array of steps that can make legitimate moves. Rooks, Bishops and Queens may iterate one step type in a move. All other pieces may only make one step per move.
        Returns:
        an array or arrays of directions where each inner array is a legitimate step.
